text: The Fizeș () is a right tributary of the river Someșul Mic in Romania. It discharges into the Someșul Mic in Gherla. Its length is and its basin size is . Lakes Cătina, Geaca, Sucutard and Țaga are located on the Fizeș. The name in Hungarian means "willow-bed". ==References== Category:Rivers of Romania Category:Rivers of Cluj County
